            "description": "The object was to design, configure and test OSPF for the core routers, using different type of routers while achieving full redundancy and priority routing for different type of packages and/or different type of routing protocols already implemented.\nUsing Foundry, Brocade and HP Procurves as core routers, covering the backbone and 2 adjacent areas, while also using implemented BGP (both internal as external), full redundancy with prioritizing traffic was achieved with OSPF learning all routes in less than 15 seconds of machine switching. The design, configuration and tests were successful and the design will be implemented in the upcoming months.",
