            "description": "Design, configure and implement an IP-VPN solution with virtual firewall for a Child day care center with (currently) 1 branch office in the north of the Netherlands. The solution entails that both centers need to be able to contact each other, access the internet, be able to access and use the servers, have remote access to either work office from anywhere via a secure interface. Possible expansion had to be taken into consideration when designing the proposed solution and configured for easy plug and play option. Design, configuration and implementation of the entire solution was assigned to me. Routing protocol chosen was RIP, version 2, with possibility to configure other protocols taken into consideration and pre-build. Routers used were Cisco 861 routers.",
