            "description": "Design a network for a financial institution with 1 main office and 4 branch offices. All locations need to have 2 connections which will serve for data and voip and possible fallback in case of down lines. Design of ip addressing range should take merger with social institution in 2nd part of 2014 into consideration for a seemless transition. Configure all routers to be able to see and connect to all offices, use DNS server at main office and all connections to be run over ip-vpn's through a virtual firewall.\nAdded as wish of client specific routing through RIP and OSPF protocols, as well as specific DHCP ranges for specific hardware equipment with specified dhcp protocols.\nDesigned as special wish by client 1 network which could be taken apart easily and go on as separate entities should the situation of a split-up still arise.\nProject delivered February 16 with added 2 months for aftercare and addition/subtraction of extra wishes.",
